1948;;No Minor Vices;;American;;Lewis Milestone;;Dana Andrews, Lilli Palmer, Louis Jourdan;;romance;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/No_Minor_Vices;;Successful pediatrician Perry Ashwell (Dana Andrews) takes his attractive wife April (Lilli Palmer) and their conservative lifestyle for granted. When he allows artist Octavio Quaglini (Louis Jourdan) into their lives to sketch their "inner selves", Octavio becomes enamoured with April and tries to steal her away from Perry.[4]